2017 NY Slip Op 64721(U)



					 
				




								ACE SECURITIES CORP. v. DB STRUCTURED PRODUCTS, INC.
							

Email  | 
								Print  |
								Comments (0)



									Motion No. M-6294, Index No. 651854/14.
								




View Case




2017 NY Slip Op 64721(U)


ACE SECURITIES CORP., ET AL., Plaintiff-Appellant,
v.
DB STRUCTURED PRODUCTS, INC., Defendant-Respondent.


Appellate Division of the Supreme Court of New York, First Department.
Decided February 21, 2017.









Plaintiff-appellant having moved for an enlargment of time to perfect the appeal from the order of the Supreme Court, New York County, entered on or about March 29, 2016.
Now, upon reading and filing the papers with respect to the motion, including the stipulation of the parties, dated December 14, 2016, which defendant-respondent consents to the relief sought in the motion, and due deliberation having been had thereon.
It is ordered that the motion is granted to the extent of enlarging the time to perfect the appeal to the September 2017 Term.







